HEADWORD: Neutralizer
<hw>Neu"tral*i`zer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or
that which, neutralizes; that which destroys, disguises, or renders
inert the peculiar properties of a body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Neutrally</ent>⟦br⟧
